              %h4 How do I join MyApnea.Org?
              %p It's easy.  Simply, sign in with your name, email, password, and birth year.  You can then visit and explore the Ready to Learn and Ready to Share pages to learn more about sleep apnea and to talk with other patients like you. If you want to join the patient-led research community you will need to read and sign the informed consent before you can share additional information about yourself and your sleep apnea.
              %h4 Why do I have to sign a consent form to participate in Ready to Research?
              %p The goal of MyApnea.Org is to actively engage thousands of people with sleep apnea to share health information needed for research to improve the health and well being of patients who suffer on a daily basis.  In order to collect your information, we need your permission.
